Step-by-step Explanation

Pairwise Comparision
	divide the numbers into pairs (odd number off to the side)
		sort pairs in smaller/bigger order
Sort the Larger Elms
	collect bigger into a new list
Recusively repeat
Insert the smaller Elms into the sorted main chain

Binary insertion Stategy
	the smalls are grouped on their corresponding bigs' position in the main chain
	
